sql:
SELECT
  birth_year,
  COUNT(*)
FROM (
  SELECT
    YEAR(ANY_VALUE(birth_dt)) AS birth_year
  FROM
    cd_customers
  WHERE
    monthly_income_amt IN (50000, 60000)
  GROUP BY
    customer_rk
  HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT monthly_income_amt) = 2
  ) AS filtered_customers_birth_dt
GROUP BY
  birth_year
